description: This dataset contains information regarding the number of enrollments by population in the New York State Donate Life Registry for the latest month. The registry is a confidential database that records a person’s consent to organ/tissue donation upon death. The database is used by donation professionals to determine a person donation status at the time of their death.  For more information, check out: www.health.ny.gov/donatelife or go to the “About” tab.
